# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation RUNDLL LAUNCHER - PowerShell Module
# Author: Timur Zinniatullin, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-18
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects Obfuscated Powershell via RUNDLL LAUNCHER
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_module/posh_pm_invoke_obfuscation_via_rundll.yml

Payload="*rundll32.exe*" Payload="*shell32.dll*" Payload="*shellexec_rundll*" Payload="*powershell*"